	) ✔ Attend and explore projects\, interactive math games & activities ━━━━
	━━━━━━━━━━━━━━ ⏳ IMPORTANT DEADLINES Registration: March 15\, 2026 Project
	 Proposal: March 22\, 2026 Sharing for families who may be interested — th
	is looks like a wonderful opportunity for kids who enjoy building\, design
	ing\, explaining ideas\, and presenting math creatively!\n\nhttps://seatod
	ay.6amcity.com/events/#/details/wsma-math-fair-2026/18305966/2026-03-29T00
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/wsma-math-fair-2026/18305
	966/2026-03-29T00
