UID:1fB7C5g_s4TVt6ElHTn1F
SUMMARY:2026 Art BFA Exhibition
DTSTAMP:20260321T224046Z
DTSTART:20260404T010000Z
DESCRIPTION:The Cornish College of the Arts at Seattle University's Art Dep
	artment is proud to present the 2026 Art BFA Exhibition\, hosted at the 9t
	h Ave Gallery in South Lake Union. This exhibition features the work of 12
